snippet.title: Waifu Impact 2 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover the secrets of the paradisiac Waifu Islands. Shoot and level up your characters in this sequel of the acclaimed Waifu Impact.
 
WAIFU IMPACT 2 is a third person shooter, adventure game with role-playing elements where you explore the Waifu Islands to unlock new characters and abilities.
 
Features:

Explore Diverse Islands: Unique climates and enemies await on each island.
Save Waifus: Collect crystals to free waifus from their prisons.
Level Up: Enhance waifus’ affinity to unlock new abilities.
Discover Secrets: Solve puzzles for hidden treasures.
Outfit Customization: Unlock stylish outfits for your waifus!

More information on:
https://www.jandusoft.com/waifuimpact2
